set-bg: img/map_2.jpg
new-page: true

> *"Not Askin' You To Never Give Up. Sometimes You Gotta Let Go... Just Don't Let Anyone Change Who You Are."*

 *- Johnny Silverhand*, 2077

This is a game of alternate history and alternate universes. While canonical accuracy is a major concern, keep in mind that the politics of Cyberpunk's deep, lore rich universe are not nearly as explored as I wish they were, and thus I needed to bend the story a bit. Nevertheless, please let the author know if there are any glaring mistakes.

For more information on the politics and government of Night City, see the "Library" page on the top left. If this is your first time playing the game, it is strongly recommended that you read at least some of this information.

- @1928_easy: Begin (easy difficulty)
- @1928_main: Begin (normal difficulty)
- @1928_hard: Begin (hard difficulty)

@1928_easy
on-arrival: difficulty = -1; resources = 4; dues = 3; rb_strength = 2500; cp_relation = 29; fp_relation = 54; dp_relation = 49; budget = 5;
go-to: 1928_main

@1928_hard
on-arrival: difficulty = 1; resources = 0; dues = 1; rb_strength = 1000; liberal_dissent = 25; left_dissent = 30; socialist_dissent = 25; industrialist_dissent = 25; fp_relation = 41; cp_relation = 16; dp_relation = 31; budget = 3;
go-to: 1928_main

@1928_main
audio: shuffle music/1928_1930/FruhlingsliedMendelssohn.mp3 music/1928_1930/AUF_HOHEN_BERGEN_noise_reduced.mp3 music/1928_1930/MarekWeber.mp3 music/1928_1930/BAUERNKAPELLE.mp3 music/1928_1933/DERLINDENBAUM_normalifped.mp3 music/1928_1933/fpurSonne_fpurFreiheit.mp3 music/1928_1933/arbeiter_marseille.mp3 music/1928_1933/Wann_wir_schreiten_Seit_an_Seit.mp3 music/1930_1933/Internationale-de_normalifped.ogg music/1928_1930/LiedDerPompadour.mp3 music/1928_1933/SofpialistenMarsch.mp3
new-page: true
go-to: main if difficulty >= 0; main.main_easy if difficulty < 0

= 2077

It’s a good day for Night City’s democracy. After recovering from the Unification War, an autocoup leading to our independence, and 4 corporate wars, we are better than ever in terms of economy.

Now, the task of the Independent party is to prepare for the next election in November. The current Conservative council is wildly unpopular among most of Night City, and therefore we stand to gain.

@election_simulation
go-to:election_simulation


